title: Quictent Galvanized Tall Raised Garden Bed Kit, 6x3x2 ft Oval Large Planting Box Rubber Strip Edging, for Vegetables Outdoor Double Strengthened by Vertical Bar and Crossbar with Liner (Dark Grey)

This large metal planter box will make your garden more artistic and funny."," 【Rubber Strip Edging】Garden bed kit include rubber strip for covering sharp egde, it is safe when you and your family growing plants, watering or plucking fruits. You can use them without any caution, even children can get close to learn and take care of plants."," 【Double Strengthened】Due to vertical bar and crossbar in the middle of ground garden box, the structure of galvanized steel raised garden bed is more stable，it has bigger capacity of weight than ohters. It won't crack and bulge at joints of 2 metal sheets, provide your plants a long-lasting home."," 【Deepened Height】Metal raised garden bed is 24\" tall, normal height is only 12\". You can add mutiple layers of material at the bottom to creat nutrient-rich soil; you can grow some deep roots vegetables or fruits, this tall garden bed can be a perfect match to short garden box."," 【Open Bottom】Open bottom of garden raised planting bed is good for drainage, plant roots won't be sick from eccessive water. Also plants' roots can obsorb variant nutrition from soil, and grow more healthily."]
